tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE leads (
    lead_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    lead_name STRING,
    lead_email STRING,
    lead_phone STRING,
    lead_criteria JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE leads (
 lead_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 lead_name TEXT,
 lead_email TEXT,
 lead_phone TEXT,
 lead_status TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE criteria (
 criteria_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 criteria_name TEXT,
 criteria_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE lead_categories (
 category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 lead_id INT,
 category_name TEXT,
 FOREIGN KEY (lead_id) REFERENCES leads(lead_id)
)

CREATE TABLE lead_criteria (
 lead_id INT,
 criteria_id INT,
 FOREIGN KEY (lead_id) REFERENCES leads(lead_id),
 FOREIGN KEY (criteria_id) REFERENCES criteria(criteria_id)
)

CREATE TABLE Leads (
    lead_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    lead_name VARCHAR(255),
    lead_email VARCHAR(255),
    lead_phone VARCHAR(15),
    lead_source VARCHAR(50),
    lead_status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE LeadCriteriaMapping (
    mapping_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    lead_id INT,
    criteria_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (lead_id) REFERENCES Leads(lead_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (criteria_id) REFERENCES Criteria(criteria_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Leads (
    lead_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    lead_name VARCHAR(255),
    lead_email VARCHAR(255),
    lead_phone VARCHAR(20),
    lead_status VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE Criteria (
    criteria_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    criteria_name VARCHAR(255),
    criteria_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE LeadCriteria (
    lc_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    lead_id UUID,
    criteria_id UUID
)

CREATE TABLE FilteredLeads (
    filtered_lead_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    lead_id UUID,
    filter_criteria_id UUID,
    filter_status VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE LeadCategories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(255),
    lead_id UUID
)
